item.title: What Is My MBTI Type
item.description: What is MBTI Myers–Briggs Type Indicator is a typology theory authored by Katharine Cook Briggs and her daughter Isabel Briggs Myers, it is based off by Carl Jung’s work, for more information, Google it, lol. Test results Before you scream and shout at your screen that tests are inaccurate, I already am aware of the problems concerning it, for example according to a section in the PDB Wiki. if you score high on Ne, it’s likely you will also score high on Se.
